description.content:
Confused about which package to buy? just message me :)


Hi there!

Are you looking for a Frontend Web Developer to build a responsive, stunning, and user-friendly website from scratch or looking for someone to redesign & develop your existing website, then you are in the right place! What you can think I can develop it for you!

I am Ismail, A Professional Frontend Web Developer providing reliable web services for a custom website since 2017.


Gig Includes:

  • Edit HTML page or CSS
  • PSD TO HTML 
  • Edit/Modify/Fix CSS
  • Edit/Modify/Fix HTML forms
  • Add/Edit forms (HTML/CSS)
  • Edit/Modify navigation & menus
  • Edit modify color schemes of the website
  • HTML to REACT
  • API integration


I will use GitHub to deploy for testing it online and also can deploy on your computer with free hosting. (Limited Time Offer)


You will gain the following advantages from me:

  1. Clean code
  2. Pixel perfect design
  3. Custom fonts and icons
  4. Responsive design for PC, Mobile, Tablet

  

 Why me?

  • Premium quality and timely results.
  • Communication throughout the whole process.


Message me and we can start discussing your project


Thanks

Regards

Muhammad Ismail

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you develop websites without design?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: For the design sense, I have developed hundreds of websites so I have vast experience in this as if you have something in mind or have reference websites then I can help out to make a great website without designing.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website will be mobile friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
For Sure, IF you want to make it responsive(mobile friendly) then you just need to mention that in our chat so I will make sure it will be good on mobile devices.
It will have some extra charges as well.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you host website after development on our domain?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: For Sure, If you need to make your website live, and you have domain and hosting purchased already then just mention this, and I will help in this but it will have some extra charges as well.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you show your Previous developed websites?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Send me a custom message, I will send you some of my developed websites, and web applications or you can also check my portfolio here on my profile page.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you do modification on the already developed site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, please send your website link along with the modification we can discuss and make a custom offer for that
